  "title": "V3DfgPeephole: Introduce PUSH_REDOR_THROUGH_OR",
  "body": "This PR introduces `PUSH_REDOR_THROUGH_OR` V3DfgPeephole pass that bases on assumption that REDOR of OR is OR of REDOR-ed arguments. This opens a way for further 1-bit bitwise reductions, for instance changing conditionals under REDOR-s to 1-bit bitwise operations.\r\n\r\nWith this change I got about 4% simulation time gain on my large design. rtlmeter `XiangShan:mini-chisel6:dhry` bench shown negligible simulation performance difference.\r\n\r\n### Tree for `t_dfg_peephole.py` test\r\n\r\nOld:\r\n```verilog\r\n    1:2: ASSIGNW 0x555557160000 <e38843> {f173dv} @dt=0x55555704a300@(G/w1)\r\n    1:2:1: REDOR 0x55555715ce70 <e38841> {f173dx} @dt=0x555557039a40@(G/w1)\r\n    1:2:1:1: OR 0x55555715cdc0 <e38840> {f173ey} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)\r\n    1:2:1:1:1: COND 0x55555715cbb0 <e38824> {f173ek} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)\r\n    1:2:1:1:1:1: SEL 0x5555572672c0 <e38821> {f173eg} @dt=0x555557039a40@(G/w1) decl[63:0]]\r\n    1:2:1:1:1:1:1: VARREF 0x5555571cf930 <e38810> {f173ea} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)  rand_a [RV] <- VAR 0x55555703ac60 <e37289> {f16ak} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)  rand_a INPUT [VSTATIC]  WIRE\r\n    1:2:1:1:1:1:2: CONST 0x555557264f00 <e36138> {f173eh} @dt=0x555557199980@(G/sw6)  6'h0\r\n    1:2:1:1:1:1:3: CONST 0x555557274a50 <e38820> {f173eg} @dt=0x555557041c80@(G/w32)  32'h1\r\n    1:2:1:1:1:2: VARREF 0x5555571cfa00 <e38822> {f173em} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)  rand_a [RV] <- VAR 0x55555703ac60 <e37289> {f16ak} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)  rand_a INPUT [VSTATIC]  WIRE\r\n    1:2:1:1:1:3: CONST 0x5555572651d0 <e38823> {f173ev} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)  64'h0\r\n    1:2:1:1:2: COND 0x55555715cd10 <e38839> {f173fl} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)\r\n    1:2:1:1:2:1: SEL 0x555557267740 <e38836> {f173fh} @dt=0x555557039a40@(G/w1) decl[63:0]]\r\n    1:2:1:1:2:1:1: VARREF 0x5555571cfad0 <e38825> {f173fb} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)  rand_b [RV] <- VAR 0x55555703ad80 <e37290> {f17ak} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)  rand_b INPUT [VSTATIC]  WIRE\r\n    1:2:1:1:2:1:2: CONST 0x5555572650e0 <e36179> {f173fi} @dt=0x555557199980@(G/sw6)  6'h0\r\n    1:2:1:1:2:1:3: CONST 0x555557274b40 <e38835> {f173fh} @dt=0x555557041c80@(G/w32)  32'h1\r\n    1:2:1:1:2:2: VARREF 0x5555571cfba0 <e38837> {f173fn} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)  rand_b [RV] <- VAR 0x55555703ad80 <e37290> {f17ak} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)  rand_b INPUT [VSTATIC]  WIRE\r\n    1:2:1:1:2:3: CONST 0x5555572652c0 <e38838> {f173fw} @dt=0x55555704aa80@(G/w64)  64'h0\r\n    1:2:2: VARREF 0x5555571cfc70 <e38842> {f173cz} @dt=0x55555704a300@(G/w1)  PUSH_REDOR_THROUGH_OR [LV] => VAR 0x555557034fc0 <e37267> {h129ai} @dt=0x55555704a300@(G/w1)  PUSH_REDOR_THROUGH_OR OUTPUT [VSTATIC]  WIRE\r\n```\r\n\r\nNew:\r\n```verilog\r\n    1:2: ASSIGNW 0x555557352460 <e57727#> {f173dv} @dt=0x555557040300@(G/w1)\r\n    1:2:1: OR 0x555557392d10 <e57724#> {f173dx} @dt=0x555557040300@(G/w1)\r\n    1:2:1:1: AND 0x555557392b00 <e57720#> {f173ek} @dt=0x555557040300@(G/w1)\r\n    1:2:1:1:1: VARREF 0x5555573960d0 <e57683#> {h105ai} @dt=0x555557040300@(G/w1)  PUSH_SEL_THROUGH_REPLICATE [RV] <- VAR 0x555557290ea0 <e39955> {h105ai} @dt=0x555557040300@(G/w1)  PUSH_SEL_THROUGH_REPLICATE [PO] OUTPUT [P] [VSTATIC]  WIRE\r\n    1:2:1:1:2: REDOR 0x555557392a50 <e57684#> {f173ey} @dt=0x55555702fa40@(G/w1)\r\n    1:2:1:1:2:1: VARREF 0x5555573961a0 <e57680#> {f16ak} @dt=0x555557040a80@(G/w64)  rand_a [RV] <- VAR 0x5555572966c0 <e40249> {f16ak} @dt=0x555557040a80@(G/w64)  rand_a [PI] INPUT [P] [VSTATIC]  WIRE\r\n    1:2:1:2: AND 0x555557392c60 <e57721#> {f173fl} @dt=0x55555702fa40@(G/w1)\r\n    1:2:1:2:1: SEL 0x555557394480 <e57716#> {f173fh} @dt=0x55555702fa40@(G/w1)\r\n    1:2:1:2:1:1: VARREF 0x555557396270 <e57701#> {f17ak} @dt=0x555557040a80@(G/w64)  rand_b [RV] <- VAR 0x5555572967e0 <e40255> {f17ak} @dt=0x555557040a80@(G/w64)  rand_b [PI] INPUT [P] [VSTATIC]  WIRE\r\n    1:2:1:2:1:2: CONST 0x55555738f1d0 <e57702#> {f173fh} @dt=0x555557037c80@(G/w32)  32'h0\r\n    1:2:1:2:1:3: CONST 0x55555738f2c0 <e57703#> {f173fh} @dt=0x555557037c80@(G/w32)  32'h1\r\n    1:2:1:2:2: REDOR 0x555557392bb0 <e57717#> {f173ey} @dt=0x55555702fa40@(G/w1)\r\n    1:2:1:2:2:1: VARREF 0x555557396340 <e57713#> {f17ak} @dt=0x555557040a80@(G/w64)  rand_b [RV] <- VAR 0x5555572967e0 <e40255> {f17ak} @dt=0x555557040a80@(G/w64)  rand_b [PI] INPUT [P] [VSTATIC]  WIRE\r\n    1:2:2: VARREF 0x555557396000 <e57725#> {f173dv} @dt=0x555557040300@(G/w1)  PUSH_REDOR_THROUGH_OR [LV] => VAR 0x555557292a20 <e40099> {h129ai} @dt=0x555557040300@(G/w1)  PUSH_REDOR_THROUGH_OR [PO] OUTPUT [P] [VSTATIC]  WIRE\r\n```",
